5. Event payload: resource ID, action, actor, policy decision, correlation ID — **içerik kopyalamaz**
6. Merkezi event type enum/katalog (`07` §12.3 kategori referansı)
7. Integration test: domain op + audit outbox aynı tx; outbox fail → rollback

